item.title: Jools Lebron filed trademark applications related to her ‘very demure’ content. Here’s what to know
item.description: “Very demure, very mindful” has become the latest vocabulary defining the internet’s summer. And TikTok creator Jools Lebron is now working to trademark uses of her now-viral words.

item.title: 2 Phoenix officers shot with 1 listed in critical condition, police say
item.description: Phoenix police say two officers have been shot and wounded by a person suspected of breaking into a car.
